    "description": "Join the Urban Company family as a Full Stack Developer in Ludhiana. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Urban Company:\nUrban Company is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Urban Company!",
